Thumbs.db

# App-specific
# index.db itself IS committed — Render's free tier has ephemeral filesystem,
# so without a pre-built index, every cold start rebuilds it from ~1400 MD
# files (~1.5s). The DB is fully derivable from data/ so it's safe to ship.
# The journal/WAL files below are runtime-only and must stay ignored.
index.db-journal
index.db-shm
index.db-wal
*.log
